# AI tool metadata (local/runtime)
# Runtime WAL output dirs created by reddb-server / examples at runtime.
# (Source-tree `crates/.../storage/wal/` is a Rust module, not a runtime
# output dir, and must remain tracked — pin the rule to top-level + the
# server crate's runtime location.)
/wal/
/crates/reddb-server/wal/
# Runtime WAL — binary, machine-local, should never be versioned.
wal.log
node_modules
# Profiling artifacts (local machine paths, contain dev stack traces)
flame-*.svg
perf.data
perf.data.old
*.pprof
.red/tmp/
